\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530581\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530581\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ogw1665702600188.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ogw1665702600188.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ogw1665702600188.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ogw1665702600188\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $fieldendmod\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ogw1665702600188___fieldendmod_263433\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__topic_d83024e1_d83025e1_d83026e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__p_d83027e1_d83028e1_d83029e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__topic_d54832e1_d54833e1_d54834e1_d54835e1_d54836e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1193191e75\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__d6203e20__entry__3\">Field name. It can optionally contain a\n                        qualified field name, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">MYFLD.MYENT</code>. If omitted,\n                        the current field is assumed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__topic_d54837e1_d54838e1_d54839e1_d54840e1_d54841e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1193191e132\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\"></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1__entry__2\">Field has not been modified. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ogw1665702600188__table_d8504e1_d8505e1_d8506e1__entry__2\">\n Field has been modified or if <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span> has been set for the current field.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__topic_d54842e1_d54843e1_d54844e1_d54845e1_d54846e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1193191e186\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__p_d83039e1_d83040e1_d83041e1\">Use in the loseFocus trigger of Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__topic_d54847e1_d54848e1_d54849e1_d54850e1_d54851e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1193191e196\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__p_d83045e1_d83046e1_d83047e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span> indicates whether the user has modified data in the field. It is set to 0 in the following circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34184e1_d34185e1_d34186e1\">When the user enters the field.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34187e1_d34188e1_d34189e1\">By resetting the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldcheck</span> function.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34190e1_d34191e1_d34192e1\">When data of a field is modified in ProcScript.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34193e1_d34194e1_d34195e1\">Each time a component is restarted (unless <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Component Behavior</span> is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Keep component definition and data in memory</code>).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34196e1_d34197e1_d34198e1\">By the following ProcScript statements\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34199e1_d34200e1_d34201e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34202e1_d34203e1_d34204e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">erase</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34205e1_d34206e1_d34207e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">release</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34208e1_d34209e1_d34210e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reload</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34211e1_d34212e1_d34213e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__li_d34214e1_d34215e1_d34216e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">store</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__p_d83048e1_d83049e1_d83050e1\">In contrast, the function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> indicates whether data has been modified during its lifetime in the component. For example, if the user modifies a field and leaves it, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span> is 1 (in the loseFocus trigger); <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> is also 1. If the user then returns to the field and leaves it again without changing it, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span> is 0, while <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> remains 1.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__section_obx_bsy_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1193191e293\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example checks the value of\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldendmod</span> , then checks to make sure that the value of the\n               field is less than 120:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ogw1665702600188__pre_cwg_csy_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger loseFocus ; (of field AGE)\nif ($fieldendmod = 1)\n if (AGE &gt;= 120)\n message \"That is far too old!\"\n return -1\n endif\nendif\nedn; loseFocus</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swr1665702599962.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldcheck</a><p>Return or set the requirement for field validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eai1665702600334.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occmod</a><p>Return the modification status of an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wbv1665702600112.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger loseFocus (Field)</a><p>Trigger that defines what happens after a user successfully leaves a field in a form component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530581\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530581\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$fieldendmod Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $fieldendmod Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited. $fieldendmod { ( Field ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Field String Field name. It can optionally contain a qualified field name, for example MYFLD.MYENT . If omitted, the current field is assumed. Return Values Table 2. Value Meaning 0 Field has not been modified. 1 Field has been modified or if $fieldendmod has been set for the current field. Use Use in the loseFocus trigger of Form components. Description The $fieldendmod indicates whether the user has modified data in the field. It is set to 0 in the following circumstances: When the user enters the field. By resetting the $fieldcheck function. When data of a field is modified in ProcScript. Each time a component is restarted (unless Component Behavior is set to Keep component definition and data in memory ). By the following ProcScript statements clear erase release reload retrieve store In contrast, the function $fieldmod indicates whether data has been modified during its lifetime in the component. For example, if the user modifies a field and leaves it, $fieldendmod is 1 (in the loseFocus trigger); $fieldmod is also 1. If the user then returns to the field and leaves it again without changing it, $fieldendmod is 0, while $fieldmod remains 1. Example: Using $fieldendmod The following example checks the value of $fieldendmod , then checks to make sure that the value of the field is less than 120: trigger loseFocus ; (of field AGE) if ($fieldendmod = 1) if (AGE >= 120) message \"That is far too old!\" return -1 endif endif edn; loseFocus Copy Related Links $fieldcheck Return or set the requirement for field validation. $occmod Return the modification status of an occurrence. trigger loseFocus (Field) Trigger that defines what happens after a user successfully leaves a field in a form component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}